Package opennlp.ccg.grammardoc

Interface Summary
Documenter A documenter that produces documentation for an OpenCCG grammar.
DocumenterContext Provides a context inside which a Documenter will execute.
 

Class Summary
AbstractDocumenter Convenience base class for documenters to extend
DocumenterFactory Factory class for creating documenters based on a predefined name.
GrammarDoc Class that implements the grammardoc ant task.
SourceGrammar Represents an OpenCCG grammar that is specified in a series of XML files.
SourceGrammarFile A file found in a source grammar.
 

Enum Summary
DocumenterName The known documenters that the documenter factory is aware of.
SourceGrammarFileType File types for source grammars.
 

Exception Summary
DocumenterException An exception thrown by a Documenter.
DocumenterNotFoundException Signals that no documenter could be found for a given name.
DocumenterSourceException An exception thrown by a Documenter because of a problem in the source grammar.
GrammarDocException An exception that occurs during the execution of GrammarDoc.
